      "additionalInformation": [
        "15 ADDITIONAL INFORMATION ON REVERSIBILITY\n\nDescription: Outer or inner wall of a residential or commercial building\nType of fixing: Steel wall anchors for mechanical fixing\nLevel of reversibility: Reversible connections with light repairable damage\nSimplicity of disassembly: Simple – requires the use of specific though common tools\nSpeed of disassembly: Speed of disassembly varies from quick to slow depending on element dimensions\nEase of handling (size and weight): Easy to manipulate (by hand (small size and limited weight): one worker should be sufficient\nRobustness of material (material resistance to disassembly): The material resists well during disassembly"
